:CourseGuide_565005802 rdf:type guide:CourseGuide ;
    sch:name "Design And Selection Of Materials In 3d Printing" ;
    sch:description "The attendance and use of this course will allow the student to know the current state of additive manufacturing techniques, as well as the criteria for an efficient design with the most suitable characteristics and materials for each project." ;
